{
  "name": "@meebox/agent",
  "version": "0.0.0",
  "private": true,
  "description": "高阶 Agent 核心：Agent 目录加载（SOUL/AGENTS/MEMORY/USER + rules）、上下文装配、模版脚手架；编排与 AutoPilot 后续接入（见 docs/arch/06-agent.md）",
